{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GrUJ1H9BDA91UZb4YK4sHv","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-24\n     2→\n     3→### epic-10 — retrospective (2026-03-24T10:15Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **CoverageToolName type fragmentation:** Provider values don't match HarnessState strings. Blocking clean provider adoption in coverage.ts. Needs tracking in Epic 14.\n     6→- **Story 10-5 density:** 17 ACs, 8 consumer files — heaviest story. Future migration epics should split by file count.\n     7→- **Dispatch maps half-measure:** Object key maps still enumerate all stacks explicitly, not caught by boundary test.\n     8→- **Pre-existing TS compilation errors (~100 lines):** Persisted across Epics 8, 9, 10. Prioritize 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors.\n     9→\n    10→### 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning — create-story (2026-03-24T10:19Z)\n    11→\n    12→- **Epic number reuse confusion:** Previous sprint had a different Epic 11 (Retrospective Integration). Current architecture-v3.md Epic 11 (Unified State) reuses the number.\n    13→- **Stub overwrite:** Existing story file was a 3-AC stub. Overwrote entirely with 19 ACs, 7 tasks.\n    14→- **Diverged from epic definition:** Deferred deletion of `.story_retries`/`.flagged_stories` to 11-3 to avoid data loss risk.\n    15→- **Circular dependency risk:** retry-state.ts → getSprintState() → migrateFromOldFormat() potential cycle.\n    16→\n    17→### 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning — dev-story (2026-03-24T10:34Z)\n    18→\n    19→- **Pre-existing test isolation problem:** Tests sharing project root's sprint-state.json interfere when run without full worker isolation. Pre-existing.\n    20→- **`dir` parameter vestigial in retry-state.ts:** Kept for backward compat but completely unused. Deliberate tech debt per story spec.\n    21→- **Pre-existing TS errors (87 total):** All from unrelated test files (bridge.test.ts, run.test.ts, teardown.test.ts, deps.test.ts).\n    22→- **Live sprint-state.json still v1:** Will auto-migrate to v2 on next getSprintState() call. Intended behavior.\n    23→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0e449f80-823c-4489-a784-b43b6c7039d6","uuid":"4cfe4706-b684-4de2-830a-370be3ed9fca","timestamp":"2026-03-24T10:38:49.208Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-24\n\n### epic-10 — retrospective (2026-03-24T10:15Z)\n\n- **CoverageToolName type fragmentation:** Provider values don't match HarnessState strings. Blocking clean provider adoption in coverage.ts. Needs tracking in Epic 14.\n- **Story 10-5 density:** 17 ACs, 8 consumer files — heaviest story. Future migration epics should split by file count.\n- **Dispatch maps half-measure:** Object key maps still enumerate all stacks explicitly, not caught by boundary test.\n- **Pre-existing TS compilation errors (~100 lines):** Persisted across Epics 8, 9, 10. Prioritize 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors.\n\n### 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning — create-story (2026-03-24T10:19Z)\n\n- **Epic number reuse confusion:** Previous sprint had a different Epic 11 (Retrospective Integration). Current architecture-v3.md Epic 11 (Unified State) reuses the number.\n- **Stub overwrite:** Existing story file was a 3-AC stub. Overwrote entirely with 19 ACs, 7 tasks.\n- **Diverged from epic definition:** Deferred deletion of `.story_retries`/`.flagged_stories` to 11-3 to avoid data loss risk.\n- **Circular dependency risk:** retry-state.ts → getSprintState() → migrateFromOldFormat() potential cycle.\n\n### 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning — dev-story (2026-03-24T10:34Z)\n\n- **Pre-existing test isolation problem:** Tests sharing project root's sprint-state.json interfere when run without full worker isolation. Pre-existing.\n- **`dir` parameter vestigial in retry-state.ts:** Kept for backward compat but completely unused. Deliberate tech debt per story spec.\n- **Pre-existing TS errors (87 total):** All from unrelated test files (bridge.test.ts, run.test.ts, teardown.test.ts, deps.test.ts).\n- **Live sprint-state.json still v1:** Will auto-migrate to v2 on next getSprintState() call. Intended behavior.\n","numLines":23,"startLine":1,"totalLines":23}}}
